rows.label: tlk000001_msg0001
rows.name:
Never thought I'd see the day you'd
be riding the Maelstrom, Rex.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0002
rows.name:
Suppose it just goes to show how far
you've come as a salvager, eh?

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0003
rows.name: Well, I'm proud of you, lad.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0004
rows.name:
Now, are you all set? We're setting
sail soon as you're ready to board.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0008
rows.name:
That's what I like to hear!
Come on then, hop on!

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0009
rows.name:
We're heading into uncharted territory
for this job, you know. I'm getting
goose pimples just thinking about it!

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0010
rows.name:
Well, I say that, but don't worry. You
can always come back here any time
you think it's getting hairy.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0011
rows.name:
It's not as if we're heading off to war
or anything.

rows.label: tlk000001_msg0012
rows.name:
I'm not ready to shuffle off the mortal
coil just yet, so watch how you go!
